  - guid: 5997ece3-9847-4bea-8473-c3321d25468c
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Boss
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'Yeah I mean it''s fine, you know.

        Today
        is the first time, you know, it got challenging.'
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Boss
      <Content>k__BackingField: You know, I'm a pretty easy Boss, so I don't got
        much to do usually.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Boss
      <Content>k__BackingField: The only time I really have to put in effort is during
        events.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Boss
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'There''s some where i need to fight like a dozen
        times straight, you know.

        It''s quite exhausting.'
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1028.5, y: -145}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: f04ce6da-a084-4001-b1f1-1dfefaa08752
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Boss
      <Content>k__BackingField: I don't really know that much about him, you know.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Boss
      <Content>k__BackingField: I think he's pretty young, he is also playing already
        for a long time.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Boss
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'If you want to know more,

        you can take
        a peek at his messages, you know.

        Maybe you''ll find out more.'
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
